</para>
<para id="element-59b"> 
We have discussed that magnitude of displacement and distance are different quantities. The magnitude of displacement is a measure of linear shortest distance, whereas distance is measure of actual path. As such, magnitude of average velocity <m:math> 
              <m:mrow> 
